{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/install-kakaotalk/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>한국에서 가장 많이 사용하는 인스턴트 메신저인 카카오톡은 안타깝게도 Ubuntu를 지원하지 않습니다. 따라서 Wine을 사용하여 Windows용 카카오톡 PC를 설치할 수 밖에 없습니다.</p>\n<p>나중에 참고할 수 있도록 간단하게 기록을 남깁니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"wine-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wine-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"wine 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Wine 설치</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-32bit-architecture-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-32bit-architecture-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"1 32bit architecture 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 32bit Architecture 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> dpkg --add-architecture i386</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-apt-repository-key-다운로드-및-등록\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-apt-repository-key-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%8F-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\"2 apt repository key 다운로드 및 등록 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Apt repository key 다운로드 및 등록</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -nc https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/winehq.key\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> winehq.key</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-wine-repository-등록\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-wine-repository-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\" aria-label=\"3 wine repository 등록 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Wine repository 등록</h2>\n<p>※ Wine 4.5 이상부터는 libfaudio0 패키지가 필요한데, Ubuntu 19.10 이하에서는 제공되지 않습니다. 따라서 <code class=\"language-text\">cybermax-dexter/sdl2-backport</code> PPA를 추가해야합니다. 등록한 PPA들은 <strong>소프트웨어 &#x26; 업데이트</strong> 앱에서 기타 소프트웨어 탭에서 관리할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-add-repository <span class=\"token string\">'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ bionic main'</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> add-apt-repository ppa:cybermax-dexter/sdl2-backport</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"4-wine-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-wine-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"4 wine 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Wine 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> update\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --install-recommends winehq-stable</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"5-wine-환경-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-wine-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"5 wine 환경 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Wine 환경 설정</h2>\n<p>혹시 모를 호환성 이슈를 막기 위해 32bit 프로그램만 실행하도록 설정하고 설정파일의 경로를 지정합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> ~/.wine\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">WINEARCH</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>win32 <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">WINEPREFIX</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>~/.wine winecfg</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Wine 설정</strong> 윈도우가 열립니다. 상황에 맞게 적절한 옵션을 설정합니다. <br>\n여기서는 화면 해상도를 192dpi로 설정했습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-한글-폰트-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%ED%95%9C%EA%B8%80-%ED%8F%B0%ED%8A%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"6 한글 폰트 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 한글 폰트 설치</h2>\n<p>미리 다운로드 받아둔 <code class=\"language-text\">gulim.ttf</code>를 wine 내부로 복사하고 레지스트리를 편집합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">cp</span> gulim.ttf ~/.wine/drive_c/windows/Fonts\n<span class=\"token function\">sed</span> -i <span class=\"token string\">'s/\"MS Shell Dlg\".*/\"MS Shell Dlg\"=\"Gulim\"/g'</span> ~/.wine/system.reg\n<span class=\"token function\">sed</span> -i <span class=\"token string\">'s/\"MS Shell Dlg 2\".*/\"MS Shell Dlg 2\"=\"Gulim\"/g'</span> ~/.wine/system.reg</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"카카오톡-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B9%B4%EC%B9%B4%EC%98%A4%ED%86%A1-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"카카오톡 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>카카오톡 설치</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-kakaotalk_setupexe-다운로드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-kakaotalk_setupexe-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"1 kakaotalk_setupexe 다운로드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. KakaoTalk_Setup.exe 다운로드</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://software.naver.com/software/summary.nhn?softwareId=GWS_000083\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://software.naver.com/software/summary.nhn?softwareId=GWS_000083</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-kakaotalk_setupexe-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-kakaotalk_setupexe-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 kakaotalk_setupexe 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. KakaoTalk_Setup.exe 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wine KakaoTalk_Setup.exe</code></pre></div>\n<p>또는 파일탐색기를 열고 exe에 우클릭하여 <strong>Wine Windows Program Loader로 열기</strong>를 선택할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이어서 설치를 진행합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-시스템-트레이-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%8B%9C%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%9C-%ED%8A%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 시스템 트레이 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 시스템 트레이 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> gnome-shell-extension-top-icons-plus</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치가 끝난 후, <strong>기능 개선</strong> 앱에서 확장 탭을 열고 <strong>Topions plus</strong>를 활성화합니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.winehq.org/Wine_User%27s_Guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wiki.winehq.org/Wine_User%27s_Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ubuntuhandbook.org/index.php/2020/01/install-wine-5-0-stable-ubuntu-18-04-19-10/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://ubuntuhandbook.org/index.php/2020/01/install-wine-5-0-stable-ubuntu-18-04-19-10/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hiseon.me/linux/ubuntu/ubuntu-kakaotalk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://hiseon.me/linux/ubuntu/ubuntu-kakaotalk/</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"한국에서 가장 많이 사용하는 인스턴트 메신저인 카카오톡은 안타깝게도 Ubuntu를 지원하지 않습니다. 따라서 Wine을 사용하여 Windows용 카카오톡 PC를 설치할 수 밖에 없습니다. 나중에 참고할 수 있도록 간단하게 기록을 남깁니다. Wine…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#wine-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">Wine 설치</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#1-32bit-architecture-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">1. 32bit Architecture 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#2-apt-repository-key-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%8F-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">2. Apt repository key 다운로드 및 등록</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#3-wine-repository-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\">3. Wine repository 등록</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#4-wine-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">4. Wine 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#5-wine-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">5. Wine 환경 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#6-%ED%95%9C%EA%B8%80-%ED%8F%B0%ED%8A%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">6. 한글 폰트 설치</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#%EC%B9%B4%EC%B9%B4%EC%98%A4%ED%86%A1-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">카카오톡 설치</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#1-kakaotalk_setupexe-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C\">1. KakaoTalk_Setup.exe 다운로드</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#2-kakaotalk_setupexe-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">2. KakaoTalk_Setup.exe 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#3-%EC%8B%9C%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%9C-%ED%8A%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">3. 시스템 트레이 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/install-kakaotalk/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/install-kakaotalk/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ubuntu 18.04 에서 카카오톡 설치","date":"Apr 23, 2020","tags":["ReferenceDocument","Ubuntu","Wine"],"keywords":["Ubuntu","Wine","Kakotalk","우분투","카카오톡"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/install-kakaotalk/","series":[]}}}